# Propose-step generated migrations = instance-specific GROWN columns (runtime
# drift, NOT canonical). The curated migration set is the NNNN_name.sql files +
# _journal.json. Promoting a grown field to canonical is a deliberate, human-
# gated ontology change via the codegen path, never a raw proposal_*.sql commit.
drizzle/proposal_*.sql
